{
  "stem": "11174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To me it was paradise [SIGHS] because he didn't bother me so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was out of his [? style ?].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1928.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father went in with my grandfather and an uncle to Germany, to Berlin, because my, my, my father's youngest brother had polio on the left side-- the leg, with a hand, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So somehow it came out rumors, and some people said they're sure that in Berlin there is some professor who can cure that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandfather, and aunt, my father, and that uncle went to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stood there several weeks and the doctor, the professor wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it was a farce, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This could not be cured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they talk about operation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't make it over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We know now until-- that there was nothing to be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were there for a while, and then I was in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I so happy that my father sent, to a big boy there, money for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I was in heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then I was only about a year because I was still very young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I studied in the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then after I got bar mitzvah I came back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was quite a few years off and on in the yeshivas there in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the major learning was done in beth midrash.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "An older boy who knew good how to learn, learned with one or two or three boys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this was the style of learning mostly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had friends, but you mean from my little town?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a very close friend, was named Sertoiya, Yeshia Sertoiya, Meyer Schlesinger, Yankel Barrat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was-- they weren't always in the same age, but with the two of them, we learned together.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
